POST {{host}}/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 180000,
  "category": "Insumos",
  "description": "Compra syrup y licores"
}

###

### Registrar otro gasto
POST {{host}}/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

